        "mode": "full",
        "content": "# META \u2014 Technicals\n\n## TL;DR\n\nThe April 15\u201317 breakout long thesis at $675\u2013677 is fully invalidated. Q1 2026 earnings (Apr 29 AH) triggered a ~10% single-session collapse from $669 to ~$601\u2013603 on 9.99x relative hourly volume \u2014 institutional distribution confirmed. The prior $665 stop was breached by ~$64. Current setup: post-earnings breakdown, deeply oversold hourly, with the next actionable entry only on a dead-cat bounce into $618\u2013630 resistance before considering a short (source: decisions.json, run 20260430_141238).\n\n## Setup type\n\n**Post-earnings breakdown / dead-cat bounce watch.** Prior setup (breakout continuation) is retired. Bias is bearish medium-term; near-term bounce is the tactical expectation before continuation lower.\n\n## Key levels (as of Apr 30, 2026)\n\n| Level | Price | Significance |\n|---|---|---|\n| Current price | ~$601\u2013603 | After-earnings collapse floor; hourly swing low $601.18 |\n| Dead-cat bounce target | $618\u2013630 | Prior support ($627.61) turned resistance; Fib 38.2% at $626.10 |\n| Prior entry zone | $675\u2013677 | Invalidated \u2014 now $48\u201374 above current price |\n| Prior stop | $665 | Breached \u2014 breakout thesis dead |\n| Short stop | $645 | Invalidation for any short trade |\n| Measured-move target | $583 | Range height ($44.58) projected from $627.61 breakdown |\n| Next daily pivot low | $520.26 | Extended bear target |\n\n## Indicator state (hourly, Apr 30, 2026)\n\n| Indicator | Value | Signal |\n|---|---|---|\n| RSI-21 (hourly) | 14.7 | Deeply oversold \u2014 near-term bounce likely |\n| ADX minus_di (hourly) | 55.14 | Strong bearish momentum |\n| ADX plus_di (hourly) | 8.27 | Directional imbalance extreme |\n| Relative volume (hourly) | 9.99x | Institutional distribution confirmed |\n| Bollinger %B (hourly) | -0.993 | Price well below lower band |\n| EMA structure (daily) | Technically intact | 10 EMA > 21 EMA > 50 EMA \u2014 but hourly overrides |\n| Daily RSI-21 | 78.28 | Mildly overbought daily; caution for new longs |\n\n## Prior setup note\n\nApr 11\u201317 setup (breakout continuation, $675\u2013677 entry) moved to `recent.md` as a dated bullet. Source: signals_combined.json, run 20260430_141238.\n",
